                            | H: <emph>acylyrlar</emph>. | C: <emph>ačylyrlar</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn10" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>jaḥšyny</emph>. |
                            H: <emph>jaḥsyny</emph>. | C: <emph>jaḫšyny</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn11" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>jaḥšydy</emph>. |
                            H: <emph>jaḥsydy</emph>. | C: <emph>jaḫšydyr</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn12" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>da
                                suqlančydy</emph>. | H: <emph>da suqlancydy</emph>. | C:
                                <emph>da</emph>
                            <emph>suqlančlydyr</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn13" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>ašady da</emph>.
                            | H: <emph>asady da</emph>. | C: <emph>ašady da</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn14" type="footnote">Heb. <foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וַתִּפָּקַחְנָה</foreign>
                             . </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn15" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>ki
                                jalanɣačtylar</emph>. | H: <emph>ki jalanɣactylar</emph>. | C:
                                <emph>ki jalanɣačtyrlar</emph>. </note>
