                                <emph>da</emph>. | C: <emph>da</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn18" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>bitišin</emph>. |
                            H: <emph>bitisin</emph>. | C: <emph>any</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn19" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>ötmek</emph>. |
                            H: <emph>etmek</emph>. | C: <emph>ötmäk</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn20" type="footnote">Cf. Gen. 3:14. | TKow.01:
                                <emph>topraqtyrsen</emph>. | H: <emph>topraq sensen</emph>. | C:
                                <emph>topraqtyrsen</emph>. </note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn21" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>ošol</emph>. | H:
